rows.label: qst105302_msg002
rows.name:
ありがとう　助かった
そのくらい減れば問題ないだろう

rows.label: qst105302_msg003
rows.name:
重ねて申しわけないが念のため
ゲンブ頭部まで兵士達を
護衛してもらえないだろうか

rows.label: qst105302_msg004
rows.name: ゲンブ頭部までの護衛よろしく頼むよ

rows.label: qst105302_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, we are most grateful to you!
Now we should have safe passage
to the Crown.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0002
rows.name:
We will send out a squad as soon as
we've gathered enough troops.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes...I'm afraid we haven't been able
to secure the proper numbers yet,
what with the disturbance.

rows.label: qst105302_msg0004
rows.name:
Truly, you are a tremendous
boon to us all!

rows.label: qst105302_msg0005
rows.name:
Could I entreat you to escort our
squad to the Genbu Crown and
see that they come to no harm?

rows.label: qst105302_msg0101
rows.name:
Please, escort our squad to the
Genbu Crown and see that they
arrive safely.
